Commit: `8ffe8f7 feat(senseweave): execute production arc targets [T-008@20260416T054258Z]`

What changed:
- Added phase-level production target payloads on the procedural arc.
- Commissioning now records arc elapsed/cycle timing.
- Score-tree composition now builds a per-section `production_arc` plus `arc_phase_contour`.
- Tracker compilation applies phase targets into scene metadata and automation, including density, dynamic/master amp, spatial lanes, compression, SenseWeave, and synthesis metadata.
- Added regression coverage for the five-phase 5-minute proxy contour and tracker scene production metadata.

